<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idb89f0921-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea" identifier="/us/usc/t5/s6363"><num value="6363">§ 6363.</num><heading> Establishment of leave banks</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Each agency that establishes a leave bank program under section 6362 shall establish 1 or more leave banks in accordance with regulations prescribed by the Office of Personnel Management.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idb89f0922-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/100/566/s2/a">Pub. L. 100–566, § 2(a)</ref>, <date date="1988-10-31">Oct. 31, 1988</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/102/2839">102 Stat. 2839</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
